    <entry>
      <title>001-前端学习整和01</title>
      <link href="/2022/12/31/001-%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%95%B4%E5%92%8C01/"/>
      <url>/2022/12/31/001-%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%95%B4%E5%92%8C01/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="第一篇"><a href="#第一篇" class="headerlink" title="第一篇"></a>第一篇</h2><h3 id="什么是网页？"><a href="#什么是网页？" class="headerlink" title="什么是网页？"></a>什么是网页？</h3><ul><li>​    网页是一个文件扩展名为.html的文件</li><li>​    注：网页只能通过浏览器访问阅读</li></ul><h3 id="什么是HTMl？"><a href="#什么是HTMl？" class="headerlink" title="什么是HTMl？"></a>什么是HTMl？</h3><ul><li>HTMl是用来描述网页的一种语言<ul><li>​    HTML即超文本标记语言（Hyper Text Markup Language）</li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="web（网页）的组成部分"><a href="#web（网页）的组成部分" class="headerlink" title="web（网页）的组成部分"></a>web（网页）的组成部分</h3><ul><li>HTML结构</li><li>CSS表现</li><li>JS行为</li></ul><hr><h2 id="第二篇"><a href="#第二篇" class="headerlink" title="第二篇"></a>第二篇</h2><h3 id="HTMl的基本语法"><a href="#HTMl的基本语法" class="headerlink" title="HTMl的基本语法"></a>HTMl的基本语法</h3><ol><li><p>常规标签（双标签）</p><ul><li><p>语法：</p><ul><li><p><code>&lt;标签名 属性1=&quot;属性值&quot; 属性2=&quot;属性值&quot;&gt;内容&lt;/标签名&gt;</code></p></li><li><p>例如：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ol</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;A&quot;</span> <span class="attr">start</span>=<span class="string">&quot;2&quot;</span>&gt;</span>li<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p>空标签（单标签）</p><ul><li><p>语法：</p><ul><li><p><code>&lt;标签名 属性1=&quot;属性值&quot; 属性2=&quot;属性值&quot; /&gt;</code></p></li><li><p>例如：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;1.png&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul></li></ol><hr><h2 id="第三篇"><a href="#第三篇" class="headerlink" title="第三篇"></a>第三篇</h2><h3 id="文档类型声明标签"><a href="#文档类型声明标签" class="headerlink" title="文档类型声明标签"></a>文档类型声明标签</h3><ul><li><p>作用：</p><ul><li>告诉浏览器使用哪个<strong>HTML版本</strong>来 显示网页</li></ul></li><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="keyword">html</span>&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 采用HTML5版本来显示网页 --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>注意：</p><ul><li><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE&gt;</code>声明位于文档中最前面的位置，处于<code>&lt;html&gt;</code>标签之前</li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="lang语言种类"><a href="#lang语言种类" class="headerlink" title="lang语言种类"></a>lang语言种类</h3><ul><li><p>定义：</p><ul><li>规定元素内容的语言</li></ul></li><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">&quot;en&quot;</span>&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- &quot;en&quot;代表英语，&quot;zh-CN&quot;代表中文 --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="字符集"><a href="#字符集" class="headerlink" title="字符集"></a>字符集</h3><ul><li><p>定义：</p><ul><li>字符集是多个字符的集合，以便计算机能够识别和存储文字</li></ul></li><li><p>作用：</p><ul><li>规定HTML文档应该使用哪种字符编码</li></ul></li><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span>/&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- &quot;UTF-8&quot;也被称为万国码 --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="基本的HTML页面结构"><a href="#基本的HTML页面结构" class="headerlink" title="基本的HTML页面结构"></a>基本的HTML页面结构</h3><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/xy055878/markdownSource@main/images/202212311634081.png" alt="image-20221231162533409"></p><hr><h2 id="第四篇"><a href="#第四篇" class="headerlink" title="第四篇"></a>第四篇</h2><h3 id="HTML常用标签"><a href="#HTML常用标签" class="headerlink" title="HTML常用标签"></a>HTML常用标签</h3><h4 id="注释标签"><a href="#注释标签" class="headerlink" title="注释标签"></a>注释标签</h4><ul><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 这是一个注释 --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h4 id="标题标签"><a href="#标题标签" class="headerlink" title="标题标签"></a>标题标签</h4><ul><li><p>特点：</p><ul><li>加粗</li><li><p>独占一行</p></li><li><p>数字越大，文本越小</p></li></ul></li><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hn</span>&gt;</span>内容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">hn</span>&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- n∈[1,6] --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h4 id="段落标签"><a href="#段落标签" class="headerlink" title="段落标签"></a>段落标签</h4><ul><li><p>特点：</p><ul><li>独占一行</li></ul></li><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>我是一个段落标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h4 id="换行标签"><a href="#换行标签" class="headerlink" title="换行标签"></a>换行标签</h4><ul><li><p>作用：</p><ul><li>强制换行</li></ul></li><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h4 id="文本化格式标签"><a href="#文本化格式标签" class="headerlink" title="文本化格式标签"></a>文本化格式标签</h4><ul><li><p>作用：</p><ul><li>突出重要性，使目标内容比普通文字更重要。</li></ul></li></ul><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/xy055878/markdownSource@main/images/202212311721381.png" alt="image-20221231172134293"></p><h4 id="lt-div-gt-和-lt-span-gt-标签"><a href="#lt-div-gt-和-lt-span-gt-标签" class="headerlink" title="&lt;div&gt;和&lt;span&gt;标签"></a><code>&lt;div&gt;</code>和<code>&lt;span&gt;</code>标签</h4><ul><li><p>定义：</p><ul><li>这两个标签是没有语义的，他们就是一个盒子，用来装内容的</li></ul></li><li><p><code>&lt;div&gt;</code>标签的特点和语法：</p><ul><li><p>特点：</p><ul><li>独占一行</li></ul></li><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span>童话书<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span>1997</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>效果：</p><p><div>童话书</div>1997</p></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p><code>&lt;span&gt;</code>标签的特点和语法：</p><ul><li><p>特点：</p><ul><li><font color='red'>不</font>独占一行</li></ul></li><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span>童话书<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span>1997</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>效果：</p><p><span>童话书</span>1997</p></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="lt-hr-gt-标签"><a href="#lt-hr-gt-标签" class="headerlink" title="&lt;hr&gt;标签"></a><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code>标签</h4><ul><li><p>作用：</p><ul><li>创建一条水平线</li></ul></li><li><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hr</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>…未完成</p><hr><h2 id="第五篇"><a href="#第五篇" class="headerlink" title="第五篇"></a>第五篇</h2><h3 id="HTML常用特殊字符"><a href="#HTML常用特殊字符" class="headerlink" title="HTML常用特殊字符"></a>HTML常用特殊字符</h3><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/xy055878/markdownSource@main/images/202212311721376.png" alt="image-20221231172101210"></p><div class="note info flat"><p>你也可以查看W3School上面的列表：<a href="http://www.w3school.com.cn/tags/html_ref_entities.html">http://www.w3school.com.cn/tags/html_ref_entities.html</a></p></div><h3 id="Emmet语法-速查表"><a href="#Emmet语法-速查表" class="headerlink" title="Emmet语法 速查表"></a>Emmet语法 速查表</h3><h4 id="1-调用方法"><a href="#1-调用方法" class="headerlink" title="1. 调用方法"></a>1. 调用方法</h4><blockquote><p><strong>Emmet使用<font color=green>Tab</font>作为自动生成HTML代码的触发器。</strong></p></blockquote><div class="note info flat"><p>提示：Emmet语法在遇到<code>空格</code>时将停止解析</p></div><h4 id="2-相关"><a href="#2-相关" class="headerlink" title="2. 相关"></a>2. 相关</h4><blockquote><p>后代：&gt;</p></blockquote><hr><p><strong>缩写</strong>：<code>div&gt;ul&gt;li</code></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>兄弟：+</p></blockquote><hr><p><strong>缩写</strong>：<code>div+p+bq</code></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>上级元素：^</p></blockquote><hr><p><strong>缩写</strong>：<code>div+div&gt;p&gt;span+em^bq</code></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>缩写</strong>：<code>div+div&gt;p&gt;span+em^^bq</code></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>分组：（）</p></blockquote><hr><p><strong>缩写</strong>：<code>div&gt;(header&gt;ul&gt;li*2&gt;a)+footer&gt;p</code></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">header</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">header</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">footer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">footer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>缩写</strong>：<code>(div&gt;dl&gt;(dt+dd)*3)+footer&gt;p</code></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">footer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">footer</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>重复多份：*</p></blockquote><hr><p><strong>缩写</strong>：<code>ul&gt;li*5</code></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span